Aashna Sheth studied Computer Science at the University of Washington for both her B.S. and M.S. Through her minor in Comparative History, she became especially interested in intersections of culture, history, and technology. Prior to this project, she worked on research that explored the metadata associated with the Chronicling America newspaper dataset.
